Preheat oven to 375 degrees F. Bring water and margarine to boil in large saucepan. Stir in stuffing mix; cover. Remove from heat; let stand 5 min. Stir egg and 1/2 cup of the cheese into stuffing mixture until blended. Spoon into greased 9-inch pie plate. Sprinkle with remaining 1/4 cup cheese. Bake 20 min. or until lightly brown and cheese on top is melted.